Halo! Saya sedang belajar Slim Framework PHP secara bertahap.
Berikut adalah roadmap belajar saya:

FASE 1 → Fondasi Slim
    1.1 → Routing Dasar (GET, POST, PUT, PATCH, DELETE) ✅
    1.2 → Request & Response ✅
    1.3 → Route Parameter & Query String ✅
    1.4 → Middleware Dasar ✅
    1.5 → Error Handling

FASE 2 → Database & ORM
    2.1 → Koneksi Database MySQL
    2.2 → Eloquent ORM (Laravel DB di Slim)
    2.3 → Migration & Seeder
    2.4 → CRUD dengan Eloquent

FASE 3 → REST API
    3.1 → Konsep REST API
    3.2 → JSON Response
    3.3 → API Routing (Resource)
    3.4 → CRUD API (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
    3.5 → Validasi Input
    3.6 → Error Response Standard

FASE 4 → Authentication
    4.1 → Register & Login API
    4.2 → JWT Token
    4.3 → Protected Route (Middleware Auth)
    4.4 → Refresh Token

FASE 5 → Best Practice & Finishing
    5.1 → Struktur Folder MVC
    5.2 → Repository Pattern
    5.3 → Environment (.env)
    5.4 → Testing API dengan Thunder Client
    5.5 → Deploy ke Server

=== PROGRESS SAYA ===
✅ Selesai  

=== SETUP PROJECT SAYA ===
- OS        : Windows
- Server    : Laragon
- PHP       : 8
- Framework : Slim Framework v4
- Folder    : C:\laragon\www\schola-slim
- Struktur  :
    public/
        index.php       ← entry point
    belajar/
        fase-1/
            1.1-routing-dasar/
                get.php
                post.php
                put.php
                patch.php
                delete.php
            1.2-request-response/
                request.php
                response.php
            1.3-route-parameter-query-string/
                route-parameter.php
                query-string.php
            1.4-middleware-dasar/
                middleware-global.php
                middleware-route.php
                middleware-group.php

=== CATATAN PENTING ===
- Setiap file route di-require di public/index.php
- Sudah pakai $app->addBodyParsingMiddleware()
- Setiap sub fase dibuat file terpisah

Tolong lanjutkan mengajar saya dari fase 1, 1.4 → Middleware Dasar
Gunakan bahasa yang santai, step by step, dan langsung praktek!